me to be a value stock at this point. I'll have to consider that if I reenter,
I'll have to be watching it more closely than I otherwise would have expected.
Meanwhile, my preference is for stocks now where I believe earnings will be up
in next six months. (That doesn't seem to be AMAT, given management's current
outlook.)
